<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>예약 환자 접수</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen p-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">예약 환자 접수</h1>
            <a href="reception-list.html" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700">
                목록으로 돌아가기
            </a>
        </div>

        <form action="/staff/reception/1/complete" method="POST" class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <input type="hidden" name="reservationId" value="1">
            
            <div class="bg-indigo-50 border-b border-indigo-100 p-6 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shadow-sm border border-indigo-100">
                        <i data-lucide="user" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">홍길동</h2>
                            <span class="px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800">
                                ONLINE
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <i data-lucide="phone" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                            <span>010-1234-5678</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">현재 상태</div>
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 font-semibold text-sm">
                        <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                        예약 (접수 대기)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="p-8 space-y-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">예약 정보</h3>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">예약 일시</div>
                                <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">2025-03-05 09:00</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">진료과 / 전문의</div>
                                <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">내과 / 김원장</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <i data-lucide="file-text" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                            <div class="w-full">
                                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">증상 및 메모</div>
                                <div class="text-slate-800 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-sm leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">
                                    두통, 어지러움
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">추가 정보 입력</h3>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                    <i data-lucide="home" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                                    주소
                                </label>
                                <input
                                    type="text"
                                    name="address"
                                    value="서울시 강남구 테헤란로 123"
                                    placeholder="환자 주소를 입력하세요"
                                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none text-sm"
                                />
                            </div>
                            
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                    <i data-lucide="alert-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                                    특이사항 (알레르기, 과거 병력 등)
                                </label>
                                <textarea
                                    name="specialNotes"
                                    placeholder="접수 시 참고할 특이사항을 입력하세요"
                                    rows="4"
                                    class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none text-sm resize-none"
                                >페니실린 알레르기</textarea>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-end gap-3">
                    <button type="button" onclick="history.back()" class="px-6 py-3 bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                        취소
                    </button>
                    <button type="submit" class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        접수 완료 처리 (RECEIVED)
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
